
TWO PATTERNS PEOPLE OFTEN CONFUSE
--------------------------------------------
DECORATOR:
LoggingDecorator  <>----  PaymentProcessor
     |
     v  (inherits)
ProcessorDecorator -----> process()
     ^
     |
MetricsDecorator  <>----  PaymentProcessor
RetryDecorator    <>----  PaymentProcessor
--------------------------------------------
CHAIN OF RESPONSIBILITY:
BaseHandler  <>----  BaseHandler(next)
    ^
    |
 FraudCheck
